OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'must be allowed to
OL,4,Cstand' for parliament, Labour MP argues
OL,6,FThe Labour Party should allow former
OL,7,Fcabinet minister Andy Burnham to stand
OL,8,Ffor parliament, an MP from Kent has
OL,9,Fargued.
OL,11,FTony Vaughan told ITV Meridian's The
OL,12,FLast Word the Greater Manchester mayor
OL,13,Fhad "the best polling of any UK
OL,14,Fpolitician" and it is "really
OL,15,Fimportant that there is a contest
OL,16,Finvolving all of the talents of the
OL,17,Fparty".
OL,26,@uD@EOUvD@KO]vD@WOUyD@FO]
