OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778782268
OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'must be allowed to
OL,4,Cstand' for parliament, Labour MP argues
OL,6,F"Were it to be the case a leadership
OL,7,Felection were triggered, and were it
OL,8,Fto be the case that another MP resigns
OL,9,Fin a seat that Andy Burnham seeks to
OL,10,Fcontest, the party has to let him
OL,11,Fstand and contest that so the by-
OL,12,Felection could occur."
OL,14,FThe Folkestone and Hythe MP added
OL,15,Fthat, if a leadership contest is
OL,16,Ftriggered, there is "no point leaving
OL,17,Fout our strongest candidates".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@VO]xD@UOUyD@]O]
