OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'must be allowed to
OL,4,Cstand' for parliament, Labour MP argues
OL,6,FMr Burnham was blocked from contesting
OL,7,Fthe Gorton and Denton by-election by
OL,8,FLabour's National Executive Committee
OL,9,F(NEC) in January.
OL,11,FAs a serving directly-elected metro
OL,12,Fmayor, he needs the approval of the
OL,13,FNEC to stand for a Commons seat.
OL,15,FTony Vaughan is among more than 90
OL,16,Fbackbench MPs to publicly call for Sir
OL,17,FKeir Starmer to set- out a timetable
OL,18,Ffor his departure from Downing Street,
OL,19,Ffollowing major local election losses
OL,20,Ffor Labour.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
