OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'must be allowed to
OL,4,Cstand' for parliament, Labour MP argues
OL,6,FThe Kent MP claimed that "people want
OL,7,Fchange but the change is not happening
OL,8,Fquickly enough".
OL,10,FVeteran Conservative MP, Sir Roger
OL,11,FGale, told The Last Word that Sir Keir
OL,12,FStarmer is a "perfectly decent man"
OL,13,Fbut "not a strong prime minister".
OL,15,FThe Herne Bay and Sandwich MP said:
OL,16,F"This situation is awful because it's
OL,17,Fbad for the country, it's bad for the
OL,18,Feconomy, it's bad for parliament.
OL,19,FWe've got a zombie government."
OL,26,@nD@ZOUpD@OO]tD@NOUtD@cO]uD@EOUuD@aO]xD@
OL,26,AAOU{D@_O]
