OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'must be allowed to
OL,4,Cstand' for parliament, Labour MP argues
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat MP Lee Dillon argued
OL,7,FAndy Burnham was "taking the
OL,8,Felectorate for granted" by "assuming
OL,9,Fhe would win a seat" before he had
OL,10,Feven been selected for one.
OL,12,F"There needs to be a change of focus
OL,13,Ffrom the Labour government", the
OL,14,FNewbury MP added.
OL,16,FBrighton and Hove city councillor, Sue
OL,17,FShanks, said that on the doorstep in
OL,18,Fthe local election campaign in West
OL,19,FSussex, she picked up an "anything but
OL,20,FLabour" attitude from voters.
OL,26,@oD@ROUpD@WO]pD@\OUqD@TO]tD@AOUuD@[O]{D@
OL,26,AZOU|D@GO]
