OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'must be allowed to
OL,4,Cstand' for parliament, Labour MP argues
OL,6,FCllr Shanks added: "People have just
OL,7,Fgot fed up with things that they were
OL,8,Ftold were going got change and
OL,9,Fhaven't."
OL,11,FEast Worthing and Shoreham MP, Tom
OL,12,FRutland, and Gillingham and Rainham
OL,13,FMP, Naushabah Khan, both resigned as
OL,14,Fministerial aides this week to
OL,15,Fpublicly call for Sir Keir Starmer to
OL,16,Fgo.
OL,18,FMr Rutland would publicly support Wes
OL,19,FStreeting in a potential future
OL,20,Fleadership contest, ITV News Meridian
OL,21,Funderstands.
OL,26,@nD@TOU
