OL,3,CAndy Burnham 'must be allowed to
OL,4,Cstand' for parliament, Labour MP argues
OL,6,FA source close to the Sussex MP said
OL,7,Fthe former health secretary had "made
OL,8,Fa principled decision" and can win the
OL,9,F"battle of ideas".
OL,11,FAt least nine backbench Labour MPs
OL,12,Ffrom the South and South East have
OL,13,Fpublicly stated they want a new Labour
OL,14,Fleader.
OL,16,FITV Meridian's monthly political
OL,17,Fprogramme, The Last Word, is on ITV1
OL,18,Fat 10.45pm on Thursday, 14 May 2026.
OL,19,FWatch the full episode below or on
OL,20,FITVX and YouTube
